desc_short	-----								Grab some friends and dive into the jungles of CONGO - a co-op, horror action game. Set in the dark and haunting jungle, light-fearing demons attack from the shadows. Work together as a team to find rescue from wave after wave of intense attack by scavenging an array of weapons and items.							
developer									The Innocent Devils										
